p.d: This magazine is the story of Olympic Sailing, as the world’s best strive to compete on the world’s greatest sports stage and claim their medals at the Olympic Games. Dedicated to Olympic sailing, Sailing to Tokyo follows the long journey and defining moments in athletes’ careers as they dream to make Olympic history.
